# GeoCollab Repo Audit & Fix Plan

Full audit of `f:\SWDEV\VRTerra\geocollab` against [MASTER-PLAN.md](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/MASTER-PLAN.md) and `@webxr-geocollab` skill.

## Identified Issues

### 🔴 Critical Bugs (App will not load)

| # | File | Issue |
|---|------|-------|
| 1 | `index.html:8` | Socket.IO **v2.5.0** loaded from CDN, but [package.json](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/package.json) has `socket.io@4.8.3` on the server. **Version mismatch = connection failure.** NAF 0.12 ships with socket.io v2 adapter — but server runs v4. |
| 2 | `index.html:21` | `serverURL` is hard-coded to `https://192.168.1.14`. Should auto-detect from `window.location` so it works on any LAN. |
| 3 | `terrain.js:12-16` | `new Cesium.CesiumTerrainProvider(...)` — this constructor was **deprecated** in Cesium 1.104+. Must use `Cesium.CesiumTerrainProvider.fromUrl()` (async). Also, `url: '/terrain'` points to an empty directory — **will 404 immediately and crash Cesium Viewer.** |
| 4 | `terrain.js:8` | `cesiumContainer.style.display = 'none'` — Cesium **cannot render** into a hidden div (canvas has 0×0 size). Need `position: absolute; left: -9999px` instead. |
| 5 | `terrain.js:20` | `scenegraph: false` — not a valid Cesium Viewer option. Will throw warning. |
| 6 | `terrain.js:32` | `new THREE.CanvasTexture(canvas)` — `THREE` is not directly exposed by A-Frame 1.6. Must use `AFRAME.THREE.CanvasTexture`. |
| 7 | `terrain.js:35-48` | `AFRAME.registerComponent('cesium-terrain', ...)` is called **inside** `DOMContentLoaded` — by that time A-Frame may have already parsed the HTML and tried to use the component. Must register **before** scene parse. |
| 8 | `map-tools.js:38` | `THREE.MathUtils.generateUUID()` — same issue, should be `AFRAME.THREE.MathUtils.generateUUID()`. |
| 9 | `index.html:9` | NAF v0.12.0 from **unpkg CDN** — but the Master Plan says **air-gap / zero internet**. All CDN deps will fail offline. |

### 🟡 Missing Features (per Master Plan)

| # | Feature | Status |
|---|---------|--------|
| 10 | **Floor plane** — removed during Phase 3 edits | Missing entirely. Players fall through the void. |
| 11 | **Measurement tool** — distance between two points on terrain | Not implemented (only pin dropper exists). |
| 12 | **Voice.js** — dedicated voice setup file from project structure | Missing. Voice relies only on NAF `audio: true` with no mic-permission button. |
| 13 | **App.js** — scene logic / VR entry from project structure | Missing. Everything is inline or scattered. |
| 14 | **Avatar.js** — avatar template + sync from project structure | Missing. Avatar is just a sphere with no hand tracking. |
| 15 | **ui.css** — VR overlay UI styles | Missing. No CSS file exists. |
| 16 | **VR Comfort** — snap turn, vignette, teleport locomotion | Not implemented. Only `wasd-controls` + `look-controls` (desktop only). |
| 17 | **Coordinate labels on grid** | Grid overlay is just a wireframe plane with no labels. |
| 18 | **`dem_data/` directory** | Missing from project structure. |
| 19 | **`start` script in package.json** | `main` points to `index.js` not [server.js](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/server.js). No `start` script. |
| 20 | **Online terrain/map data** | User requests OSM + online terrain sources for testing (instead of local-only). |

### 🟢 Architecture Issues

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 21 | Server hard-codes port 443 — needs `sudo`/admin on most systems. Should use env var or 3000. |
| 22 | No `.gitignore` — `node_modules/` and `certs/` will be committed. |
| 23 | No error handling in server.js at all (no try/catch on cert read, no process error handlers). |

---

## Proposed Changes

### Server & Config

#### [MODIFY] [server.js](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/server.js)
- Fix port to `process.env.PORT || 3000` (not 443)
- Add error handling for cert reads
- Add process-level error handlers
- Log the actual LAN IP dynamically

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/package.json)
- Set `"main": "server.js"`
- Add `"start": "node server.js"` script

#### [NEW] [.gitignore](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/.gitignore)
- Ignore `node_modules/`, `certs/`, `logs/`

---

### Frontend — Fix Critical Bugs

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/public/index.html)
- Remove all CDN `<script>` tags — serve libs from `node_modules` or local `vendor/` folder
- Auto-detect `serverURL` from `window.location.origin`
- Add missing floor plane back
- Add `<a-scene screenshot>` for screenshot support
- Add mic-permission button overlay before VR entry
- Fix Socket.IO version to match server

#### [MODIFY] [terrain.js](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/public/js/terrain.js)
- **Switch from local `/terrain` to online sources** per user request:
  - Use `Cesium.createWorldTerrainAsync()` for Cesium Ion world terrain (free tier)
  - Use OSM Buildings imagery provider
- Fix `display: none` → offscreen positioning
- Remove invalid `scenegraph` option
- Fix `THREE` → `AFRAME.THREE`
- Register `cesium-terrain` component **outside** DOMContentLoaded
- Add measurement tool (click two points, show distance)

#### [MODIFY] [map-tools.js](file:///f:/SWDEV/VRTerra/geocollab/public/js/map-tools.js)
- Fix `THREE` → `AFRAME.THREE`
- Add coordinate labels to grid overlay
- Improve pin dropper to work with map plane (not just table)

---

