## Verification Plan

### Automated (Browser Test)
1. Start server: `cd f:\SWDEV\VRTerra\geocollab && node server.js`
2. Open `https://localhost:3000` in browser
3. Verify: page loads without console errors
4. Verify: A-Frame scene renders (sky, table, map, floor visible)
5. Verify: Cesium terrain loads from online sources (OSM/Ion)
6. Verify: Socket.IO connects (check "user connected" in server logs)

### Manual (User)
1. Open two browser tabs to `https://localhost:3000` — verify both connect and see each other's avatar
2. When Quest 3 is available, test full VR entry with controllers
